review_blob: 12oz. bottle.  Notes of roasted nuts and leather.  Very sweet up front, but finishes smoky.  Medium to full body, very creamy.  Highly enjoyable.
12 oz can.  Sweet, sticky mouthfeel.  Light fruit.  There are great canned beers out there, and 21As design and creativity are admirable, but taste always leaves something to be desired.
beer_name: 21st Amendment Special Edition Allies Win The War
